name: Jalina
content:
Jalina was a female Tarasin, who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.
Jalina was a member of the Hiironi irstat, a Tarasin tribe that lived on the planet Cularin. During the time of the Clone Wars, Jalina was present at a briefing in the jungles of Cularin, where Major Xirossk of the Cularin Militia sent the heroes of Cularin on a mission to find the Wyrd.
